  <name>me3</name>
  <summary>Mod framework for FromSoftware games</summary>
  <description>
    <p>me3 is a mod framework for FromSoftware games including Dark Souls 3,
    Sekiro, Elden Ring, Armored Core VI, and Elden Ring Nightreign.</p>
    <p>It manages mod profiles and launches games via Proton with DLL injection
    for filesystem-level mod loading on Linux.</p>
